      • addObjectTableEntry

        public void addObjectTableEntry(HwmfObjectTableEntry entry)
        Adds an record of type HwmfObjectTableEntry to the object table. Every object is assigned the lowest available index-that is, the smallest numerical value-in the WMF Object Table. This binding happens at object creation, not when the object is used. Moreover, each object table index uniquely refers to an object. Indexes in the WMF Object Table always start at 0.(将类型为HwmfjectTable entry的记录添加到对象表中。在WMF对象表中，每个对象都被分配了最小的可用索引，即最小的数值。这种绑定发生在对象创建时，而不是使用对象时。此外，每个对象表索引唯一地引用一个对象。WMF对象表中的索引始终从0开始。)
        Parameters:
        entry - the object table entry(条目-对象表条目)

      • applyObjectTableEntry

        public void applyObjectTableEntry(int index)
        Applies the object table entry(初始化对象表条目)
        Parameters:
        index - the index of the object table entry (0-based)(index -对象表条目的索引（从0开始）)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - if the index is out of range(java.lang. IndexOutOfBoundsResponse-如果索引超出范围)
        java.util.NoSuchElementException - if the entry was deleted before(java.util. NoSuchElement异常-如果该条目之前已被删除)

      • unsetObjectTableEntry

        public void unsetObjectTableEntry(int index)
        Unsets (deletes) the object table entry for further usage When a META_DELETEOBJECT record (section 2.3.4.7) is received that specifies this object's particular index, the object's resources are released, the binding to its WMF Object Table index is ended, and the index value is returned to the pool of available indexes. The index will be reused, if needed, by a subsequent object created by another Object Record Type record.(取消（删除）对象表条目以供进一步使用当接收到指定此对象特定索引的Meta_DELETEObserver记录（2.3.4.7部分）时，该对象的资源将被释放，与其WMF对象表索引的绑定结束，并将索引值返回到可用索引池。如果需要，该索引将由另一个对象记录类型记录创建的后续对象重新使用。)
        Parameters:
        index - the index (0-based)(index -指数（从0开始）)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - if the index is out of range(java.lang. IndexOutOfBoundsResponse-如果索引超出范围)
